('bbfab19e-70e2-4fb7-bb99-86b6b05c239f'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Chamoy Sauce, El Chilerito 355ml', 'Size: 330 ML Sweet, sour, spicy, the holy trinity of Mexican flavor in a bottle. Salsa Chamoy 355ml is a bold and tangy chamoy sauce perfect for drizzling on fruit, snacks, and even cocktails. It’s the ultimate party essential! 🌶️ Brand: El Chilerito 🌶️ Sweet, tangy, and mildly spicy 🌶️ Classic chamoy made for fruit, chips, and drinks 🌶️ Loved for micheladas, mangonadas, and candy dips 🌶️ 355ml bottle – perfect for sharing or stocking up. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
