('70718368-c21e-4e6f-835c-05eee4c59866'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Whole Ancho Chili, El Fresno', 'Deeply flavorful and gently smoky, El Fresno Whole Dried Ancho Chilies (sun-dried poblanos) add rich color and mild, fruity heat to classic Mexican dishes. Rehydrate them for sauces and moles, or grind them to boost marinades, stews, and rubs. 🌶️ Brand: El Fresno 🌶️ 100 % whole dried ancho chiles 🌶️ Mild heat with notes of raisin, cocoa, and smoke 🌶️ Perfect for moles, adobo sauces, chili pastes, soups, and braises 🌶️ Generous 1 kg bulk pack – ideal for chefs, restaurants, and serious chili lovers. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
