('4db0c7f2-2ba4-4ab2-8161-b980a89a7fc6'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Whole Pasilla Chili,El Fresno', 'Deep, rich, and slightly fruity, El Fresno Whole Dried Pasilla Chilies are essential for traditional Mexican cooking. Known for their dark color and complex flavor, these chilies add depth and mild heat to sauces, moles, soups, and stews. 🌶️ Brand: El Fresno 🌶️ 100% whole dried pasilla chiles 🌶️ Mild heat with raisin-like sweetness and smoky undertones 🌶️ Perfect for moles, enchilada sauces, and slow-cooked dishes 🌶️ 1 kg bulk pack, ideal for chefs, restaurants, and chili lovers. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
