('a6481252-4c19-40f8-b134-11caabf1389e'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Artisanal Hot Sauce Basket, La Meridana', 'A beautifully wrapped gift straight from the heart of Mexico! 🇲🇽 This artisanal basket is filled with four bold and fruity habanero hot sauces from La Meridana, each crafted with authentic Mexican ingredients and packed in a vibrant handwoven basket. 🔥 Includes 4 full-size bottles (150 ml each): 🥭 Mango Habanero – Sweet, tangy, and tropical 🍑 Papaya Habanero – Smooth heat with a fruity twist 🌿 Green Habanero – Earthy, zesty, and herbaceous 🌶 Red Habanero – Classic, bold, and spicy 🎁 Presented in a colorful handwoven basket, making it the perfect gift for chili lovers , foodies, or anyone who loves bold flavors. 💯 100% made in Mexico, 100% unforgettable flavor.'),
