('2f36cf44-d8ce-427d-894b-dbfc96109f67'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Whole Cascabel Chili', 'Known for their round shape and signature rattle sound, El Fresno Whole Dried Cascabel Chilies offer a mild, nutty flavor with subtle smokiness. These unique chilies are ideal for salsas, sauces, and slow-cooked dishes that need gentle heat and rich flavor. 🌶️ Brand: El Fresno 🌶️ 100% whole dried cascabel chiles 🌶️ Mild heat with earthy, slightly smoky notes 🌶️ Excellent for blending into salsas, soups, sauces, and marinades 🌶️ 1 kg pack, great for bulk use in kitchens, restaurants, or catering. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
