('f604af54-4118-401d-907b-54292a533233'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Maizena Corn Starch', 'The original and trusted kitchen essential in every Mexican household. Maizena’s corn starch is your secret ingredient for creating dishes that are crispier, fluffier, and creamier, from fried favorites to velvety soups and baked treats. 🌽 Made with natural corn 🥞 Perfect for fluffy pancakes &amp; soft cakes 🍗 Adds crispness to fried foods 🥣 Thickens sauces, soups &amp; desserts effortlessly 👩🍳 A versatile pantry staple for sweet or savory recipes. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
