('ec2639da-dcc7-44c4-aced-5303078f2f83'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Chocolate Abuelita', 'Warm, nostalgic, and full of flavor, Abuelita is the taste of Mexican tradition in every cup. These classic chocolate tablets are infused with cinnamon and spices, creating a rich, frothy drink when melted into hot milk. Whether it’s for chilly mornings or festive evenings, Abuelita brings comfort straight from la cocina. As sweet as grandma''s hug! 🍫 Authentic Mexican-style hot chocolate ☕ Just melt into milk and whisk until frothy 🌶️ Subtle hints of cinnamon and spice 👵🏼 A beloved recipe passed down for generations 📦 6 tablets per pack – makes 6 full liters. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
