('3ee9b933-4879-4ed5-afc5-d10c6e478c0e'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Chamoy Sauce, El Chilerito 1lt', 'Sweet, sour, spicy, the holy trinity of Mexican flavor in a bottle. El Chilerito Salsa Chamoy is a bold and tangy chamoy sauce perfect for drizzling on fruit, snacks, and even cocktails. It’s the ultimate party essential! 🌶️ Brand: El Chilerito 🌶️ Sweet, tangy, and mildly spicy 🌶️ Classic chamoy made for fruit, chips, and drinks 🌶️ Loved for micheladas, mangonadas, and candy dips 🌶️ 1L bottle – perfect for sharing or stocking up. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
