('787ba3af-b2ff-4696-85fe-740b9ca0b6f8'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Guacamole Salsa, La Costeña', 'Creamy, zesty, and ready to pour — La Costeña Guacamole Salsa brings together the rich texture of avocado with a mild spice for a perfect finishing touch to tacos, nachos, burgers, or grilled veggies. No chopping, no mashing — just open and enjoy! 🌶️ Brand: La Costeña 🌶️ Smooth avocado-based salsa 🌶️ Mild heat with fresh lime and onion flavor 🌶️ Perfect for tacos, nachos, salads, or dipping 🌶️ 445 g bottle – easy to pour and serve. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
