('3aa331ad-507c-4cb9-8e55-80626ad60135'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Homestyle Sauce, La Costeña', 'A classic, fire-roasted flavor straight from the Mexican kitchen. La Costeña Salsa Casera Mexicana (Tatemada) is made with roasted tomatoes, onions, and chilies to give you that authentic, homemade taste. A must-have for tacos, eggs, or grilled meats. 🌶️ Brand: La Costeña 🌶️ Roasted tomato-based Mexican-style salsa 🌶️ Medium heat with a smoky, homemade flavor 🌶️ Ideal for topping tacos, eggs, grilled chicken or steak 🌶️ 250 g bottle – rich, thick texture. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
