('365e882a-22e1-4903-b4a4-19246f0a8407'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Piñera Sauce,La Conspiración', 'Sweet meets heat in this tropical sensation, Salsa Piñera blends juicy pineapple with bold habanero for a vibrant salsa that’s fruity, fiery, and unforgettable. Ideal for grilled shrimp, tacos al pastor, or even spooned over cream cheese. 🌶️ Brand: La Conspiración 🌶️ Made with real pineapple &amp; habanero 🌶️ Tropical, tangy, and spicy 🌶️ Delicious on seafood, white meats, or chips 🌶️ 250 g glass jar. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
