('3fcac2d1-65ae-4d46-8593-8c843779286d'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Bichi Sauce, La Conspiration', 'Creamy, zesty, and undeniably fresh — Salsa Bichi is a smooth blend of serrano chiles, cilantro, and crema that brings a herbaceous heat to your dishes. Perfect for tacos, grilled corn, seafood, or as a dip for chips. 🌶️ Brand: La Conspiración 🌶️ Made with serrano chiles, cilantro &amp; cream 🌶️ Mild heat with rich, creamy texture 🌶️ Great on tacos, tostadas, or veggies 🌶️ 250 g glass jar. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
