('40d1f547-99c9-4441-a1be-1d5b773516af'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Mojito Green Sauce, La Conspiración', 'A refreshingly bold twist on salsa, Salsa Mojito Verde by La Conspiración combines roasted chiles with fresh spearmint for a zesty, herbaceous kick. Bright, slightly smoky, and completely unique, it’s a flavorful topping or marinade for tacos, grilled veggies, seafood, or even salads. 🌿 Brand: La Conspiración 🌿 Made with spearmint &amp; roasted chiles 🌿 Herbal, smoky, and tangy flavor profile 🌿 Perfect for seafood, salads, or chicken 🌿 250 g glass jar. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
