('ec8453e9-0cd1-42dc-a12b-a9792c85bbe7'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Three Chili Sauce, La Conspiración', 'Creamy, smoky, and packed with flavor, Salsa Tres Chiles by La Conspiración blends three smoked chili peppers with smooth cream for a rich and bold Mexican sauce. It’s the perfect balance of heat and indulgence, ready to elevate tacos, sandwiches, grilled meats, or even breakfast eggs. 🔥 Brand: La Conspiración 🔥 Made with 3 smoked chili varieties 🔥 Cream-based with a velvety texture 🔥 Great with grilled meats, tacos, or as a dip 🔥 250 g glass jar. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
