('de5567ea-4ace-43a8-80f0-8a440e51450f'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Cholula Original Hot Sauce', 'A true Mexican classic. Cholula Original Hot Sauce delivers a well-balanced, zesty blend of piquín and arbol peppers with a signature flavor that enhances rather than overpowers. Smooth, smoky, and just the right amount of heat, it’s the go-to bottle for flavor lovers everywhere. 🌶️ Brand: Cholula 🌶️ Iconic wooden cap &amp; authentic recipe 🌶️ Mild-to-medium heat with a smoky finish 🌶️ Great for eggs, tacos, pizza, popcorn &amp; more 🌶️ 150 ml glass bottle. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
