('dee5cd2f-4d3a-433f-9889-24493689ee4b'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Tajín Chamoy Hot Sauce', 'A tangy-sweet twist with a mild kick — Tajín Chamoy Sauce brings together fruity chamoy flavor, chili, and lime in a smooth, pourable blend. Perfect for topping fruits, snacks, drinks, or even desserts, it adds a bold, mouthwatering zing that’s hard to resist. 🍑 Brand: Tajín 🍑 Classic chamoy flavor with chili and lime 🍑 Mild heat with sweet &amp; tangy undertones 🍑 Ideal for fruit bowls, gummy candy, mangonadas &amp; rim dips 🍑 455 ml squeeze bottle for easy use. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
