('88347455-4971-4965-90ae-9b1ae9ad6083'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Valentina Salsa Picante (Original Yellow Label)', 'A beloved classic in every Mexican kitchen, Valentina Salsa Picante Original is famous for its tangy, mild-to-medium chile flavor and smooth texture. It’s not just hot sauce—it’s a way of life. Splash it over popcorn, fruit, soups, chips, eggs, and everything in between! 🌶️ Brand: Valentina 🌶️ Mild to medium heat with tangy chile flavor 🌶️ Versatile and smooth, not overly vinegary 🌶️ Perfect for snacks, soups, and street-style dishes 🌶️ 370 ml plastic bottle, iconic yellow label. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
