('3660cf57-5561-415c-8fc9-96652ec24441'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Valentina Salsa Picante Very Hot (Black Label)', 'Mexico’s cult-favorite hot sauce, now in its extra-hot black-label version! Valentina Salsa Picante “Muy Picante” delivers a thicker, tangy chile-arbol heat that clings to everything from tacos and popcorn to micheladas. 🌶️ Brand: Valentina 🌶️ Extra-hot black label (“Muy Picante”) 🌶️ Tangy chile-arbol flavor with a lingering burn 🌶️ Perfect for tacos, fruit, chips, soups &amp; cocktails 🌶️ 370 ml plastic bottle – pour on the heat! Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
