('250fb701-90eb-4b82-b073-48a23010c2d0'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Habanero and Pineapple smoked Hot Sauce, El Yucateco', 'Turn up the heat with a tropical twist, El Yucateco Habanero y Piña Asada Hot Sauce combines the fiery kick of habaneros with the smoky-sweet flavor of grilled pineapple. Perfect for BBQs, tacos al pastor, or glazing meats with a bold fruity punch. 🍍 Brand: El Yucateco 🍍 Made with roasted pineapple &amp; habanero peppers 🍍 Sweet, smoky, and spicy all in one 🍍 Great on grilled meats, seafood, or pizza 🍍 120 ml glass bottle. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
