('60e2dd79-e41f-4163-ae59-4ca3e1186cbb'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Marisquera Red Hot Sauce, El Yucateco', 'Crafted especially for seafood lovers, El Yucateco Marisquera Roja Hot Sauce is a zesty, bold blend designed to elevate shrimp, oysters, ceviche, and more. With its tangy flavor and subtle heat, this sauce brings a splash of the Mexican coast to every bite. 🦐 Brand: El Yucateco 🦐 Ideal for seafood, ceviche, and cocktails 🦐 Balanced with spice, tang, and a hint of citrus 🦐 A coastal favorite with authentic flavor 🦐 150 ml glass bottle. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
