('17390074-cc01-4984-ade5-7820ea0cf7a1'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Habanero anf Coffee Hot Sauce, El Yucateco', 'A bold blend for true flavor seekers — El Yucateco Habanero y Café Hot Sauce fuses the smoky heat of habanero with the rich depth of coffee. A unique, slightly sweet and roasty sauce that adds character to everything from grilled meats to savory breakfast plates. 🌶️ Brand: El Yucateco 🌶️ Made with habanero chili and coffee 🌶️ Smoky, earthy, and mildly sweet 🌶️ Ideal for grilled dishes, eggs, or BBQ marinades 🌶️ 120 ml glass bottle. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
