('66c66cfe-b450-4473-8c82-823bd1a4ba35'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Habanero & Ghost Chili Hot Sauce, El Yucateco', 'Warning: This one’s not for the faint of tongue ! 🌶💀 El Yucateco combines the fierce heat of habanero peppers with the fiery intensity of ghost chilies to create a hot sauce that delivers a slow burn and bold flavor in every drop. Perfect for those who crave extreme heat with character , this sauce amps up tacos, wings, soups, or even cocktails. If you dare, try it on your eggs for breakfast and see how your day starts 🔥 ✅ Made in Mexico ✅ No artificial colors ✅ Heat Level: 🌶🌶🌶🌶 (EXTREME) Net Weight: 120ml. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
