('a2f35597-9674-478e-8fd0-63befcd9ba3a'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Habanero Sauce Sampler, La Meridana', 'Spice up your kitchen with authentic Mexican heat! 🇲🇽 This boxed sampler from La Meridana brings together four unique habanero hot sauces , each made with real fruit, bold spices, and zero compromises. 🔥 Inside the box: 🍑 Papaya Habanero – Sweet heat with a tropical finish 🥭 Mango Habanero – Fruity fire that dances on the tongue 🌿 Green Habanero – Zesty, fresh, and slightly herbal 🌶 Red Habanero – The classic kick with full chili flavor 💡 Perfect for gifting or sampling – whether you’re new to hot sauce or already addicted. ✔️ Vegan · Gluten-Free · Made in Mexico · 4 x 150 ml bottles. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
