('73868ed3-f7ca-43ad-9931-0bd129eda913'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Hot Habanero Sauce Sampler Pack, La Meridana', 'Taste the full spectrum of Mexican heat with this vibrant sampler pack from La Meridana . Whether you''re gifting or just can’t choose one favorite, this set brings the perfect mix of smoky, fruity, and fiery flavors straight from Mexico. 🔥 Includes 4 x 50 ml bottles: 🌶 Papaya Habanero – Fruity sweetness meets tropical fire 🌶 Mango Habanero – A juicy twist with bold spice 🌶 Green Habanero – Zesty, herbaceous and sharp 🌶 Red Habanero – Classic, fiery and full-bodied 🎁 Perfect for gifting, sampling, or spicing up every meal. 💯 Made in Mexico. 100% authentic. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
