('ee3e4aea-1a20-490e-90d4-cb4d6dda079a'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Lucas Muecas Mango (Spicy Mango Lollipop with Chili Powder)', 'A sweet and spicy treat with a tropical twist! Lucas Muecas Mango combines a mango-flavored lollipop with tangy chili powder for dipping fun. Dip, lick, repeat, this is Mexican candy the way it’s meant to be: bold and addictive. 🌶️ Brand: Lucas 🌶️ Mango-flavored lollipop with chili powder dip 🌶️ Sweet, sour, and spicy flavor combo 🌶️ Includes 10 pieces (24 g each) 🌶️ Net weight: 240 g. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
