('51ae4d72-d4a0-41ee-8556-50113ecec0f6'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Pelon Pelo Rico Tamarind', 'A classic favorite with a fun twist! Pelon Pelo Rico Tamarindo is a tangy, spicy tamarind-flavored candy that you push up through a soft, squeezable container—creating the signature “hair” effect. Sweet, sour, and seriously fun to eat! 🌶️ Brand: Pelon Pelo Rico 🌶️ Tamarind-flavored candy with a touch of chili 🌶️ Soft texture and unique push-up dispenser 🌶️ Includes 12 individual containers (30 g each) 🌶️ Total net weight: 360 g. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
