('968f1bba-949e-417b-a14c-1e745707a634'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Pulparindo Mango (Tamarind Candy with Mango Flavor)', 'The perfect twist on a Mexican favorite! Pulparindo Mango blends the classic sweet-sour-spicy tamarind candy with a tropical mango kick. Made from natural tamarind pulp, it’s chewy, tangy, and full of bold flavor in every bite. 🥭 Brand: De la Rosa 🥭 Tamarind candy with chili, salt, and natural mango flavor 🥭 Sweet, sour, spicy, and tropical, all in one! 🥭 Includes 20 individually wrapped pieces 🥭 Net weight: 280 g. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
