('dc81184d-8f9b-4b38-9b04-17c16779e859'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Mazapan Original, De la Rosa', 'A true classic! De la Rosa Mazapán is Mexico’s beloved peanut candy, known for its soft, crumbly texture and rich nutty flavor. Made from crushed peanuts and sugar, it melts in your mouth and brings sweet nostalgia with every bite. 🥜 Brand: De la Rosa 🥜 Original peanut marzipan candy since 1950 🥜 Soft, crumbly texture with bold peanut flavor 🥜 Contains 12 individually wrapped pieces 🥜 Net weight: 336 g. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
