('9062dc56-5993-417c-8ac1-07db97ff3b3d'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Lucas Muecas Chamoy', 'Sweet, sour, and irresistibly spicy! Lucas Muecas Chamoy is a classic Mexican lollipop dipped in tangy chamoy powder. It’s the perfect mix of flavors that dance on your taste buds with every lick. Fun to eat and packed with flavor. 🌶️ Brand: Lucas 🌶️ Chamoy-flavored lollipop with tangy chili powder 🌶️ Unique push-up style candy you can dip again and again 🌶️ Includes 10 individual pieces , great for sharing or party favors 🌶️ A popular Mexican treat for spicy candy lovers. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
