('11863256-5fda-4ebf-ab74-9bd04f58e8bb'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Palebola Tama-Roca Tamarind Candy', 'Spicy, salty, and sweet, Palebola Tama-Roca is an iconic Mexican tamarind candy that packs a punch! Made with natural tamarind, chili, and salt, it’s a bold treat for those who crave intense, tangy flavors. A nostalgic favorite since 1975. 🌶️ Brand: Palebola Tama-Roca 🌶️ Natural tamarind candy with chili and salt 🌶️ A true Mexican classic, spicy, sour, and addictive! 🌶️ Contains 12 individually packed pieces 🌶️ Net weight: 720 g. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
