('a687ca38-1c29-4d37-b612-ae01dd03a864'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Barritas Strawberry,Marinela', 'Soft, fruity, and deliciously nostalgic, Marinela Barritas Fresa are tender cookie bars filled with a sweet strawberry jam center. A classic Mexican snack perfect for school lunches, coffee breaks, or an anytime treat. 🍓 Brand: Marinela 🍓 Soft-baked bars with real strawberry filling 🍓 Each box contains 12 individually wrapped bars 🍓 Great for on-the-go snacking or sharing 🍓 Net weight: 402 g. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
