('48609398-7665-49f4-b6f4-b3b341927afc'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Whole Pasilla Chili, El Fresno', 'Bring authentic flavor to your kitchen with El Fresno Whole Dried Pasilla Chilies . Known for their dark color and rich, mildly spicy profile, these chilies are perfect for creating depth in traditional Mexican dishes like moles, sauces, and soups. 🌶️ Brand: El Fresno 🌶️ 100% whole dried pasilla chiles 🌶️ Mild heat with a deep, raisin-like sweetness 🌶️ Ideal for moles, enchilada sauces, and slow-cooked recipes 🌶️ 100 g pack, great for home cooks exploring Mexican cuisine. Available from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
